# King Uniforms Email Configuration
# Copy this to .env in your project root for local development

# Gmail SMTP Configuration
EMAIL_USER=your-email@kinguniforms.net
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-gmail-app-password

# Example:
# EMAIL_USER=emperez@kinguniforms.net
# EMAIL_PASSWORD=xxxx xxxx xxxx xxxx

# Instructions:
# 1. Replace with your actual Gmail address
# 2. Generate Gmail App Password (not regular password):
#    - Go to Google Account settings
#    - Security → 2-Step Verification (must be enabled)
#    - App passwords → Generate password for "Mail"
#    - Use the 16-character password generated
# 3. Save this file as .env (remove .template from filename)
# 4. Add .env to .gitignore to keep credentials secure
